  <p>With 5G and IoT devices on the rise, edge computing pushes data processing closer to the source, reducing latency and improving user experiences in real time.</p>

  <h3 class="mt-4 text-warning">🔐 Cloud Security and Compliance</h3>
  <p>As data breaches grow more sophisticated, cloud providers offer robust encryption, zero-trust models, and compliance tools to protect sensitive data and meet regulations.</p>

